title: Unearthed.S01E01.Devils.Roots.480p.HDTV.x264-mSD
description:
This season, an historic drought hits Oregon and then winter comes early, bringing the truffle supply to an all-time low with prices predicted to hit an all-time high. With increased competition between the foragers and even more diggers seeking riches, the truffle men of Oregon will be pushed to their limits to survive. The foragers are: Roy Siegfried and Terry Drazdhoff (aka The Old Timers), who have invented every secret to finding truffles over the last 40 years; Ty Hale & Levy Schwartzendruber (aka The Young Generation), who learned from the Old Timers but broke out on their own, covering up to 600 acres a day and netting close to $100,000 a season; Richie Maxfield (aka The Lone Wolf), a self-proclaimed truffle engineer, who must find a way to get water on one of his prized patches; and Justin Anderson (aka Oregon's Truffle Kingpin), a woodsman and an opportunist, who moved his massive black truffle operation into Falls City 10 years ago.
